<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/index.css" />
		<title>Document</title>
	</head>
	<body class="bg-ghost-white">
		<header class="mt-20 flex flex-nowrap items-center justify-center">
			<svg class="-mt-8 h-10 w-10 -rotate-12 fill-orangered">
				<use xlink:href="/public/cook.svg#icon"></use>
			</svg>
			<h1 class="text-5xl font-medium text-eerie-black">Recipes</h1>
		</header>
		<div class="mt-20 flex justify-center">
			<div class="flex w-96 rounded-md shadow-lg">
				<input
					type="text"
					class="h-10 w-full rounded-l-md px-2 outline-none"
					placeholder="Search for a recipe"
				/>
				<button
					class="flex h-10 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-r-md bg-orangered duration-150 hover:bg-eerie-black"
				>
					<svg
						class="h-5 w-5 fill-ghost-white"
						aria-hidden="true"
						focusable="false"
					>
						<use xlink:href="/public/search.svg#icon"></use>
					</svg>
				</button>
			</div>
		</div>


		<div class="mt-20 flex flex-col items-center">
			<% for(i=0; i<4; i++) { %>
			<div
				class="mb-5 flex h-32 w-1/2 rounded-md bg-white shadow-lg"
				href="#"
			>
				<div
					data-placeholder
					class="relative h-auto w-full overflow-hidden rounded-l-md bg-gray md:w-48"
				></div>
				<div class="ml-3 mr-3 flex w-full flex-col justify-center">
					<div
						data-placeholder
						class="relative mb-2 h-4 w-1/2 overflow-hidden rounded bg-gray"
					></div>
					<div class="mb-2 flex">
						<div
							data-placeholder
							class="relative mr-4 h-4 w-20 overflow-hidden rounded bg-gray"
						></div>
						<div
							data-placeholder
							class="relative mr-2 h-4 w-4 overflow-hidden rounded bg-gray"
						></div>
						<div
							data-placeholder
							class="relative h-4 w-7 overflow-hidden rounded bg-gray"
						></div>
					</div>
					<div>
						<% for (d=0; d<2; d++) { %>
						<div
							data-placeholder
							class="relative h-4 w-full overflow-hidden rounded bg-gray mb-1 last:mb-0"
						></div>
						<% } %>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<% } %> <% for(i=0; i<4; i++) { %>
			<a
				class="mb-5 flex h-32 w-11/12 rounded-md bg-white shadow-lg duration-150 hover:scale-105 md:w-3/4 lg:w-1/2 max-w-3xl"
				href="#"
			>
				<img
					class="h-auto w-32 rounded-l-md object-cover md:w-48"
					src="https://coffee.alexflipnote.dev/random?rnd=<%= i %>"
				/>
				<div class="ml-3 mr-3 flex w-full flex-col justify-center">
					<p class="mb-1 text-xl font-medium text-eerie-black">
						Un super gateau
					</p>
					<div class="mb-1 flex">
						<div class="mr-4 flex items-center">
							<% grade=2.4 %> <% while (grade>0) { %> <% if
							(grade>=1) { %>
							<svg
								class="h-4 w-4 fill-orangered"
								aria-hidden="true"
								focusable="false"
							>
								<use xlink:href="/public/star.svg#icon"></use>
							</svg>
							<% } else if (grade>=0.5) { %>
							<svg
								class="h-4 w-4 fill-orangered"
								aria-hidden="true"
								focusable="false"
							>
								<use
									xlink:href="/public/star-half.svg#icon"
								></use>
							</svg>
							<% } else { %>
							<svg
								class="h-4 w-4 fill-orangered"
								aria-hidden="true"
								focusable="false"
							>
								<use
									xlink:href="/public/star-empty.svg#icon"
								></use>
							</svg>
							<% } %> <% grade-- %> <% } %>
						</div>
						<div class="flex items-center">
							<svg
								class="mr-2 h-4 w-4 fill-orangered"
								aria-hidden="true"
								focusable="false"
							>
								<use xlink:href="/public/clock.svg#icon"></use>
							</svg>
							<span class="text-sm text-eerie-black">30 min</span>
						</div>
					</div>
					<p class="leading-5 line-clamp-2">
						Hic qui qui doloribus libero repellendus reiciendis.
						Sunt consequuntur omnis quia eligendi dolor itaque.
						Eligendi omnis adipisci blanditiis tempora ut. Et
						nesciunt voluptas molestias amet molestiae iste
						excepturi consequuntur. Maiores ut perferendis iste
						debitis quisquam molestias. Sunt voluptas maxime illo.
						Eum rerum aspernatur corrupti necessitatibus est. Ipsum
						tempora voluptatem doloribus. Ea ratione et voluptas qui
						libero.
					</p>
				</div>
			</a>
			<% } %>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
